      <title>瑞士央行将基准利率下调半个百分点，向瑞郎展示实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/snb-cuts-rate-by-surprise-half-point-in-show-of-force-on-franc</link>
